<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/271910305">玩游戏卡怎么判断是哪个硬件拖后腿了？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="122609945"
data-atoken="508969160"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1539312545"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/271910305/answer/508969160">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="122609945">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="508969160">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-122609945"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
