<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/35713301">外国人有哪些对中国的刻板印象会令中国人大吃一惊？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="107774128"
data-atoken="427377820"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1530030122"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/35713301/answer/427377820">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="107774128">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="427377820">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-107774128"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
